name: Lot of 2
description:
This is a lot of 2 pairs of pierced earrings.
 Included are: 
 ~ A  pair of copper filigree leaf earrings with 18mm gold-tone hooks.
 ~ A pair of earrings that features three decorative beads and a rectangular stone at the end of a two-pronged chain and one larger bead at the end of the other. The earrings have a 16mm silver-tone hook.
 These earrings are in very good pre-owned condition.
